''\n|Jeff D. Jacques\n|January 2, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4566-8}}\n|-\n|4\n|''The Art of the Comeback''\n|Glenn Greenberg\n|May 1, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4978-9}}\n|-\n|5\n|''Signs from Heaven''\n|Phaedra M. Weldon\n|May 29, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4979-6}}\n|-\n|6\n|''Ghost''\n|Ilsa J. Bick\n|July 10, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4975-8}}\n|-\n|7\n|''Remembrance of Things Past'', Book 1\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Terri Osborne\n|September 18, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4407-4}}\n|-\n|8\n|''Remembrance of Things Past'', Book 2\n|October 30, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4409-8}}\n|}\n\n==== Relaunch omnibus editions (2006\u20132010) ====\nRelaunch of the '''''S.C.E.''''' omnibus edition series. Volume numbering continued uninterrupted from the previous series.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!{{Abbr|Vol.|Volume}}\n!Title (Includes)\n!Author(s)\n!Date\n!ISBN\n|-\n|8\n|''Aftermath''{{Indent|2}}{{Small|(''{{Teal|S.C.E.}}'', {{Abbr|Nos.|Numbers}} 29{{Snd}}36)}}\n|Christopher L. Bennett, et al.{{Efn-ua|''Aftermath'' (''{{Teal|Corps of Engineers}}'', Vol. 8) (2006) by Christopher L. Bennett, Loren L. Coleman and Randall N. Bills, Robert Greenberger, Michael A. Martin and Andy Mangels, and Aaron Rosenberg.}}\n|November 21, 2006\n|{{ISBNT|1-4165-2576-9}} (print){{Brk}}{{ISBNT|1-4165-4992-7}} (ebook)\n|-\n|9\n|''Grand Designs''{{Indent|2}}{{Small|(''{{Teal|S.C.E.}}'', Nos. 37{{Snd}}42)}}\n|Dave Galanter, et al.{{Efn-ua|''Grand Designs'' (''{{Teal|Corps of Engineers}}'', Vol. 9) (2007) by Dave Galanter, Allyn Gibson, Kevin Killiany, Paul Kupperberg, David Mack, and Dayton Ward and Kevin Dilmore..}}\n|July 3, 2007\n|{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-4489-0}} (print){{Brk}}{{ISBNT|978-1-4165-7916-8}} (ebook)\n|-\n|10\n|''Creative Couplings''{{Indent|2}}{{Small|(''{{Teal|S.C.E.}}'', Nos. 43{{Snd}}49)}}\n|John S. Drew, et al.{{Efn-ua|''Creative Couplings'' (''{{Teal|Corps of Engineers}}'', Vol. 10) (2007) by John S. Drew, Glenn Greenberg, Glen Hauman and Aaron Rosenberg, David Mack, Dayton Ward and Kevin Dilmo