ance''\n|V.E. Mitchell\n|June 1992\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-77571-5}}\n|-\n|23\n|''War Drums''\n|John Vornholt\n|October 1992\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79236-9}}\n|-\n|24\n|''Nightshade''\n|Laurell K. Hamilton\n|December 1992\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79566-X}}\n|-\n|25\n|''Grounded''\n|David Bischoff\n|March 1993\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79747-6}}\n|-\n|26\n|''The Romulan Prize''\n|Simon Hawke\n|May 1993\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79746-8}}\n|-\n|27\n|''Guises of the Mind''\n|Rebecca Neason\n|September 1993\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79831-6}}\n|-\n|28\n|''Here There Be Dragons''\n|John Peel\n|December 1993\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-86571-4}}\n|-\n|29\n|''Sins of Commission''\n|Susan Wright\n|April 1994\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79704-2}}\n|-\n|30\n|''Debtors' Planet''\n|W.R. Thompson\n|May 1994\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-88341-0}}\n|-\n|31\n|''Foreign Foes''\n|Dave Galanter and Greg Brodeur\n|August 1994\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-88414-X}}\n|-\n|32\n|''Requiem''\n|Michael Jan Friedman and Kevin Ryan\n|October 1994\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-79567-8}}\n|-\n|33\n|''Balance of Power''\n|Dafydd ab Hugh\n|January 1995\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-52003-2}}\n|-\n|34\n|''Blaze of Glory''\n|Simon Hawke\n|March 1995\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-88045-4}}\n|-\n|35\n|''The Romulan Stratagem''\n|Robert Greenberger\n|May 1995\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-87997-9}}\n|-\n|36\n|''Into the Nebula''\n|Gene DeWeese\n|July 1995\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-89453-6}}\n|-\n|37\n|''The Last Stand''\n|Brad Ferguson\n|October 1995\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-50105-4}}\n|-\n|38\n|''Dragon's Honor''\n|Kij Johnson and Greg Cox\n|January 1996\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-50107-0}}\n|-\n|39\n|''Rogue Saucer''\n|John Vornholt\n|March 1996\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-54917-0}}\n|-\n|40\n|''Possession''\n|J.M. Dillard and Kathleen O'Malley\n|May 1996\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-86485-8}}\n|-\n|41\n|''The Soldiers of Fear'' \u2021{{Indent|2}}{{Small|(''{{Pink|Invasion!}}'', Book 2)}}\n|Dean Wesley Smith and Kristine Kathryn Rusch\n|July 1996\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-54174-9}}\n|-\n|42\n|''Infiltrator''\n|W.R. Thompson\n|September 1996\n|{{ISBNT|0-671-56831-0}}\n|-\n|43\n|''A Fury Scorned''\n|Pamela Sargent and Geor