 Airport|Dublin]], [[East Midlands Airport|East Midlands]], [[Edinburgh Airport|Edinburgh]], [[London Stansted Airport|London\u2013Stansted]], [[Malta International Airport|Malta]], [[Manchester Airport|Manchester]], [[Paphos International Airport|Paphos]], [[V\u00e1clav Havel Airport Prague|Prague]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Bremen Airport|Bremen]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Scandinavian Airlines]]|[[Arlanda Airport|Stockholm\u2013Arlanda]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[SmartLynx Airlines]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Orio al Serio International Airport|Bergamo]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Burgas Airport|Burgas]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Djerba\u2013Zarzis International Airport|Djerba]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Enfidha\u2013Hammamet International Airport|Enfidha]], [[Madeira Airport|Funchal]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Heraklion International Airport|Heraklion]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Lanzarote Airport|Lanzarote]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Lyon\u2013Saint-Exup\u00e9ry Airport|Lyon]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tirana International Airport N\u00ebn\u00eb Tereza|Tirana]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tivat Airport|Tivat]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Varna Airport|Varna]]<ref name=\"novatours\">{{cite web|title=Novaturas Flights en|website=Novaturas flights|url=http://flights.novatours.eu/}}</ref> \n<!-- -->\n|[[Tailwind Airlines]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Transavia France]]|[[Paris Orly Airport|Paris\u2013Orly]]<ref>http://travelnews.lv/index.php?m_id=18276&i_id=5&pub_id=118597</ref>\n<!-- -->\n|[[Turkish Airlines]]|[[Istanbul Airport|Istanbul]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Utair]] | [[Vnukovo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Vnukovo]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Uzbekistan Airways]] | [[Tashkent International Airpor