ukovo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Vnukovo]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Ryanair]] | [[Barcelona\u2013El Prat Airport|Barcelona]], [[Orio al Serio International Airport|Bergamo]], [[Berlin Sch\u00f6nefeld Airport|Berlin\u2013Sch\u00f6nefeld]], [[Brussels South Charleroi Airport|Charleroi]], [[Cologne Bonn Airport|Cologne/Bonn]], [[Dublin Airport|Dublin]], [[East Midlands Airport|East Midlands]], [[Edinburgh Airport|Edinburgh]], [[London Stansted Airport|London\u2013Stansted]], [[Malta International Airport|Malta]], [[Manchester Airport|Manchester]], [[Paphos International Airport|Paphos]], [[V\u00e1clav Havel Airport Prague|Prague]] <br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Bremen Airport|Bremen]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Scandinavian Airlines]]|[[Arlanda Airport|Stockholm\u2013Arlanda]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[SmartLynx Airlines]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Orio al Serio International Airport|Bergamo]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Burgas Airport|Burgas]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Corfu International Airport|Corfu]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Djerba\u2013Zarzis International Airport|Djerba]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Enfidha\u2013Hammamet International Airport|Enfidha]], [[Madeira Airport|Funchal]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Heraklion International Airport|Heraklion]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Lanzarote Airport|Lanzarote]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Lyon\u2013Saint-Exup\u00e9ry Airport|Lyon]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tenerife South Airport|Tenerife\u2013South]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tirana International Airport N\u00ebn\u00eb Tereza|Tirana]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Tivat Airport|Tivat]],<ref name=\"novatours\"/> [[Varna Airport|Varna]]<ref name=\"novatours\">{{cite web|title=Novaturas Flights en|website=Novaturas flights|url=http://flights.novatours.eu/}}</ref> \n<!-- -->\n|[[Tailwind Airlines]] | '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Transavia France]]|[[Paris Orly Airport|Paris\u2013Orly]]<ref>http://travelnews.lv/index.php?m_id=18276&i_id=5&pub_id=118597</ref>\n<!-- -->\n|[[Turkish Airlines]]|[[Istanbul Airport|Istanbul]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Utair]] | [[Vnukovo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Vnukovo]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Uzbekistan Airways]] | [[Tashkent International Airport|Tashkent]]\n<!-- --> \n| [[Wizz Air]] | [[Bergen Airport, Flesland|Bergen]] (ends 1 June 2020), [[Doncaster Sheffield Airport|Doncaster/Sheffield]], [[Dortmund Airport|Dortmund]], [[Eindhoven Airport|Eindhoven]], [[Kyiv International Airport (Zhuliany)|Kiev\u2013Zhuliany]], [[Luton Airport|London\u2013Luton]], [[Keflav\u00edk International Airport|Reykjav\u00edk\u2013Keflav\u00edk]] (ends 1 June 2020), [[Sandefjord Airport, Torp|Sandefjord]]<br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Barcelona\u2013El Prat Airport|Barcelona]] (ends 1 June 2020), [[Bari Airport|Bari]], [[Ramon Airport|Eilat]], [[David the Builder Kutaisi International Airport|Kutaisi]], [[Ben Gurion Airport|Tel Aviv]] (ends 1 June 2020) \n<!-- --> \n}}\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport-dest-list\n<!-- -->\n| [[Eleron]] | [[Kyiv International Airport (Zhuliany)|Kiev\u2013Zhuliany]]<ref>{{cite news |title=\"Eleron\" uzs\u0101k regul\u0101ros kravu p\u0101rvad\u0101jumus no Ukrainas uz R\u012bgu\n |url=http://riga-airport.com/lv/main/zinas/aktuali/eleron-uzsak-regularos-kravu-parvadajumus-no-ukrainas-uz-rigu |accessdate=22 Jan 2020 |work=Riga International Airport |date=15 January 2020}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n}}\n\n==Statistics==\n[[File:Letie lidojumi RIX (161) (24301691811).jpg|thumb|Check-in hall]]\n[[File:Letie_lidojumi_RIX_(120)_(23755392474).jpg|thumb|Hallway between piers ''B'' and ''C'']]\n[[File:Aeropuerto_de_Riga_-_panoramio.jpg|thumb|View of the ''B'' pier]]\n[[File:Letie_lidojumi_RIX_(245)_(24367068016).jpg|thumb|Control tower]]\n\n===Route statistics===\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=align=\n|+ '''Busiest routes from Riga (2018)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://riga-airport.com/uploads/files/Rix%