ras]]\n| continentalcup1    = [[1963-64 European Cup|European Cup]]\n| continentalcup1 qualifiers = [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n| continentalcup2    = [[1963-64 European Cup Winners' Cup|Cup Winners' Cup]]\n| continentalcup2 qualifiers = [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| continentalcup3    = [[1963-64 Inter-Cities Fairs Cup|Inter-Cities Fairs Cup]]\n| continentalcup3 qualifiers = [[Iraklis Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]\n| league topscorer   = [[Kostas Nestoridis]] (23)\n| biggest home win   = \n| biggest away win   = \n| highest scoring    = \n| matches            = 240\n| total goals        = 602\n| longest wins       = \n| longest unbeaten   = \n| longest winless    = \n| longest losses     = \n| highest attendance = \n| lowest attendance  = \n| prevseason         = [[1961\u201362 Alpha Ethniki|1961\u201362]]\n| nextseason         = [[1963\u201364 Alpha Ethniki|1963\u201364]]\n}}\n\n'''[[Super League Greece|Alpha Ethniki]]''' 1962-63 complete season\n\n{{Location map+ |Greece |width=380 |float=center |caption=Location of teams in '''1962\u201363 Alpha Ethniki''' |places=\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=37.966667 |long=23.716667 |label=<small>[[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]</small><br><small>[[Apollon Smyrni F.C.|Apollon A.]]</small><br><small>[[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]]</small><br><small>[[Fostiras F.C.|Fostiras]]</small><br><small>[[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]]</small><br><small>[[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=40.65     |long=22.9      |label=<small>[[Apollon Kalamarias F.C.|Apollon K.]]</small><br><small>[[Aris F.C. (Thessaloniki)|Aris]]</small><br><small>[[Iraklis Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]</small><br><small>[[PAOK F.C.|PAOK]]</small>}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=37.95     |long=23.633333 |label=<small>[[Ethnikos Piraeus F.C.|Ethnikos]]</small><br><small>[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]</small><br><small>[[Proodeftiki F.C.|Proodeftiki]]</small> |position=left}}\n{{Location map~ |Greece |lat=39.366667 |long=22.933333 |label=<